<h1>CostForge - Cloud Cost Intelligence Dashboard</h1>
<h3>22North Product Engineering Challenge 2026</h3>
<h2>Quick Start</h2>
<ol>
<li>Clone repo and run <code>npm install</code> in both <code>frontend</code> and <code>backend</code> directories.</li>
<li>Run <code>npm run seed</code> in the backend directory to populate the test data.</li>
<li>Run <code>npm run dev</code> in both directories to start the development servers.</li>
</ol>
